text: William Richardson (22 August 1866 - 3 January 1930) was an Australian cricketer. He played twelve first-class matches for New South Wales between 1887/88 and 1895/96. ==See also== * List of New South Wales representative cricketers ==References== ==External links== * Category:1866 births Category:1930 deaths Category:Australian cricketers Category:New South Wales cricketers Category:Cricketers from Sydney
title: William Richardson (New South Wales cricketer)
